OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMobile stolen every six    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fminutes in London - police 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Calls are being made for phone firms to
OL,6, help reduce thefts after police data   
OL,7, revealed a mobile was stolen every six 
OL,8, minutes in London last year.           
OL,10,FThe Met Police says 90,864 phones, or  
OL,11,Falmost 250 a day, were stolen in 2022. 
OL,13,FThe London mayor and Met commissioner  
OL,14,Fhave urged mobile industry bosses to   
OL,15,F"design out" incentives to steal them. 
OL,17,FMobile UK, representing UK networks,   
OL,18,Fsaid measures were in place to "combat"
OL,19,Ftheft. Leading phone makers Apple and  
OL,20,FSamsung have been asked to comment.    
